The paper focuses on developing a Questioner agent in the context of the GuessWhat?! game, which involves integrating information from visual and linguistic modalities to perform a task. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Among these, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely categories, as the paper deals with language and vision integration and uses neural network architecture to build a continuous representation of the dialogue state.
